<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-31"><a href="#Data_sources_used_for_segmentation"><span class="tocnumber">12.4</span> <span class="toctext">Data sources used for segmentation</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-32"><a href="#Internal_sources"><span class="tocnumber">12.4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Internal sources</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-33"><a href="#External_sources"><span class="tocnumber">12.4.2</span> <span class="toctext">External sources</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-34"><a href="#Companies_(proprietary_segmentation_databases)"><span class="tocnumber">13</span> <span class="toctext">Companies (proprietary segmentation databases)</span></a></li>
